name: Extra Tezuru: Paper Crane
description: Life: 5, Speed: 4, Damage: 4, Charged Shot: None. This is my humble contribution to #HENthousand. Originally, the Paper Crane would not be minted as it would be the default crane in the shmup minigame intended for the end of this small project. Now, getting this one here will add an extra life to the Paper Crane!
